This is a school project demonstrating a simple implementation of
Catmull-Clark subdivision algorithm.

Demo control:
Esc, Ctrl-Q			Exit
Space				Switch to next object
Backspace			Switch to previous object
F				Focus camera on current object
W				Toggle wireframe
+/=				Show next subdivision level
-/_				Show previous subdivision level

Camera control:
Alt-Left mouse button		Rotate camera
Alt-Middle mouse button		Pan camera
Alt-Right mouse button		Zoom camera

Homepage: http://github.com/skaslev/catmull-clark/
Author: Slavomir Kaslev <slavomir.kaslev@gmail.com>
